Package: genetrackR
Type: Package
Title: RNA-Seq Gene Expression Analysis from BAM files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Sung <wkasung@gmail.com> 
Maintainer: Alex Sung <wkasung@gmail.com>
Description: Reads BAM files. Counts read per gene and normalises these on CPM/TPM. Visualises gene expression.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    GenomicAlignments (>= 1.18.0),
    GenomicFeatures,
    GenomicRanges,
    SummarizedExperiment,
    Rsamtools,
    ggplot2
